member.name: Gdiplus.ObjectTypeIsValid
member.summary: The ObjectTypeIsValid function determines whether an element of the ObjectType enumeration represents a valid object type.
member.param: Element of the ObjectType enumeration to be tested.

returns.para: If objectType is equal to ObjectTypeInvalid, this function returns FALSE.
If objectType is equal to any other element of the ObjectType enumeration, this function returns TRUE.
